===當個創世神：Mojang的故事===
在2012年12月，其發布了[[當個創世神：Mojang的故事|當個創世神：Mojang的故事]]（Minecraft: The Story of Mojang）紀錄片，是一個關於由瑞典公司[[Mojang|Mojang]]所製作的[[當個創世神|當個創世神]]（Minecraft）開發過程的紀錄片；原先的想法是使用[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]先在2011年2月21日做出概念視頻<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ax9kmoyzl1Y |title=Minecraft Documentary HD | GameTrailers |publisher=YouTube |date=2011-02-21 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120190607/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ax9kmoyzl1Y |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並試圖籌集資金；原先目標為150,000美元，這個目標在2011年3月26日完成，到最後的募集金額是210,297美元<ref>{{cite web |author=Diana Paul |url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2pp/minecraft-the-story-of-mojang |title=Minecraft: The Story of Mojang by 2 Player Productions — Kickstarter |publisher=Kickstarter.com |date=2011-03-26 |accessdate=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6H1Q3uaPb?url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2pp/minecraft-the-story-of-mojang |dead-url=no }}</ref> ；且根據捐贈金額，將有機會將捐贈者的個人故事分享於紀錄片中。<ref>{{cite web |author=JC Fletcher on May 30th 2011 6:16PM |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/05/30/2-player-productions-looking-to-build-player-stories-into-minecr/ |title=2 Player Productions looking to build player stories into Minecraft film |publisher=Joystiq |date=2011-05-30 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110909010301/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/05/30/2-player-productions-looking-to-build-player-stories-into-minecr/ |archive-date=2011-09-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.techhive.com/article/230310/2_player_productions.html | title = 2 Player Productions: Meet the Guys Behind the Minecraft Documentary | first = David | last = Daw | date = 2011-06-15 | access-date = 2013-03-02 | work = [[PC_World|PC World]] | archive-date = 2015-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150510034002/http://www.techhive.com/article/230310/2_player_productions.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

